# Real one-off DB-access template scripts contain hardcoded live credentials
# as default fallback values (host/port/db/user/password) - confirmed during
# the 2026-07-16 pre-push secret audit. update_table.py is not caught by the
# **/temp_user* pattern above, so the whole source folder is excluded.
02_SOURCE/db_access_templates/

